title: U.S. says chemical weapons experts still not in Douma
text:
U.S. says chemical weapons experts still not in Douma 4:21am IST - 01:35 
The U.S. and Syria offering conflicting reports Tuesday as to whether global chemical weapons inspectors were able to reach the town of Douma. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
